29:48.000Z","msg":"撐拜登同民煮黨啲香港左翼人士唔知要點兜好呢"},{"pid":"cfd3c9826b250fa8d5d7b3a6e5aa6e0c75cd2ece","tid":2301223,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:36:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/24/opinion/china-us-biden.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F11%2F24%2Fopinion%2Fchina-us-biden.html&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=d8997444\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/24/opinion/china-us-biden.html</a><br />\n<br />\n閱讀繁體中文版<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20201124/china-us-biden/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fopinion%2F20201124%2Fchina-us-biden%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=67cb05f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20201124/china-us-biden/zh-hant/</a><br />\n<br />\nNYT 要柒到出文講點解會登呢篇文, 企圖合理化幫老共做推手想支持拜登要同中國合作既背景音樂.<br />\n<br />\nActing editorial page editor Kathleen Kingsbury wrote about the decision to publish this Op-Ed in Tuesday&rsquo;s edition of the Opinion Today newsletter.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/24/opinion/us-china-relations.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F11%2F24%2Fopinion%2Fus-china-relations.html&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=914be76f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/24/opinion/us-china-relations.html</a><br />\n<br />\n I began studying Mandarin that same year and took my first trip to Asia, arriving in Hong Kong just two days before Britain handed the territory over to Chinese rule ... It&rsquo;s a key sentiment &mdash; the need for multilateral cooperation &mdash; and one that Biden and his team also seem committed to. At the same time, as every president since Richard Nixon could tell you, the question with China always is: at what price?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nNYT 自己都講 &quot;到目前為止，<span class=\"red\">這篇專欄文章是<strong>中國政府</strong>關於喬&middot;拜登(Joe Biden)當選總統的唯一官方聲明</span>，超越了通常的陳詞濫調，因此我們認為它值得發表。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n不果有 D 懵撚肯定繼續死兜呢 D 係 &quot;傅瑩&quot; 自己既角度.  唔代表官方, 唔係大外宣.  傅瑩只係寫自己所想.  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國最撚鐘意呢 d 傻閪以為自己係知識份子.  最後咪利用呢 D 垃圾強推大外宣."},{"pid":"40d3c636c55b1600e87d1ffa7ca704d8fcd281b2","tid":2301223,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e0938aec5922323da9d38d6aaf9dbe83de6b49d","tid":2301223,"uid":12599,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"efb737cde2582c13134fce4e01ded236675f5cfd","tid":2301223,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T06:44:32.000Z","msg":"共贏：共產黨贏兩次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T06:54:56.000Z","msg":"兩黨共識:<br />\n<br />\n民主黨同共產黨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩邊一齊贏"},{"pid":"fc2300ba84c5264c44206bb4264b6681861ef89e","tid":2301223,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T10:47:58.000Z","msg":"有人仔，仲奶唔奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}